<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" 
    rel="stylesheet" 
    integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" 
    crossorigin="anonymous">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/caloriecalc.css">


    <body>

        
      <%- include('./common/header.ejs') %>

        
        <h1 class="title">Calorie Calculator</h1>
        <div class="calc-outer-wrap">
          <div id="form-error" style="display:none;"></div>
          <form class="calc-form" action="/home" method="post">
            <div class="form-fields"></div>
              <div class="field-outer">
                <label class="top-label">Gender</label>

                <select required placeholder="Gender"name="gender" id="gender">
                  <option value="" disabled selected>Select Your Gender</option>
                  <option value="Male">Male</option>
                  <option value="Female">Female</option>
                  </select>
                <label class="top-label">Age</label>
                <div class="field-items">
                  <div class="field field-large">      
                <input type="text" name="age" id="age" inputmode="numeric" pattern="[0-9]*" placeholder="Enter your age">
              </div>
              </div>

              <label class="top-label">Height (CM)</label>
              <input type="text" name="height" id="height" inputmode="numeric" pattern="[0-9]*" placeholder="Enter your height">


              <label class="top-label">Weight (KG)</label>
              <input type="text" name="weight" id="weight" inputmode="numeric" pattern="[0-9]*" placeholder="Enter your weight">


              <div class="form-check">
                <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="radio" value="0">
                <label class="form-check-label" for="radio">
                  Sedentary / Basal Metabolic Rate
                </label>
              </div>
              <div class="form-check">
                <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="radio" value="1">
                <label class="form-check-label" for="radio">
                  Lightly Active
                </label>
              </div>
              <div class="form-check">
                <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="radio" value="2">
                <label class="form-check-label" for="radio">
                  Active
                </label>
              </div>
              <div class="form-check">
                <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="radio" value="3">
                <label class="form-check-label" for="radio">
                  Very Active
                </label>
              </div>
              <p class="radioP">*see Level of Activity below for more info</p>
            <button class="submit-button" type="submit">Calculate</button>
           <p>  <% if(calories > 0){ %>
              Your basal metabolic rate is: <%= calories %> 
            <% } else{ %>  
              <h1></h1>
           <% } %>
          </p>
          </div>
          </form>
      </div>
        <h2 class="subtitle">Further Information</h2>
        <div class="info-container">
        <div class="info-div">
        <h3>Gaining or Losing</h3>
        <p>Gaining or losing weight is a simple concept. Eating less calories than the daily amount you burn will lead to losing weight. If you eat more than you burn, you will gain weight.</p>
        <p>It is recommended if you are trying to go up or down weight to aim for a change of 500 calories, depending on your goals. It is estimated that by cutting 500 calories daily will contribute to losing up to 0.5kg weekly</p>
      </div>
      <div class="info-div">
        <h3>Level of Activity</h3>
        <p>Sedentary/Base Rate - This is if you do not burn any calories daily and reflects how much your body will burn each day depending on current weight, height and gender</p>
        <p>Lightly Active - General exercise 1 to 3 times a week</p>
        <p>Active - Exercising 3 to 5 times a week</p>
        <p>Very Active - Intense activity 6 to 7 times a week</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="info-container">
      <div class="info-div">
        <h3>Nutrients</h3>
        <p>It is recommended that your daily calorie intake is ranges from - 45 to 65% carbs, 20 to 35% from fats and around 10 - 35% from protein</p>

      </div>
      <div class="info-div">
        <h3>Warning</h3>
        <p>Although it may seem like a good idea to lose weight quickly, NEVER drastically cut your calories. Calories are essential to our body and the many daily functions that take place inside us. Cutting drastically can make it harder to lose weight and cause health problems</p>

      </div>
      </div>

        
          

    

    </body>


</html>